genresAdvancedInfo.name: slovenske chvaly
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Slovenske chvaly is a genre of Christian music that originated in Slovenia. It is characterized by its use of traditional Slovenian folk music and lyrics that praise God and celebrate the Christian faith. The genre has been influenced by various other forms of Christian music, including gospel, hymns, and contemporary Christian music.
